<div class="t me06 x16 h2d y119a ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recitation, but fully copied in the daily life of all concerned. </div><div class="t ma28 x3e h4 y1e0c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE SURPLUS DONATIONS during the present quarter will be used in the </div><div class="t m64c x73 h4 y150c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">most needy foreign fields. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
